<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Your Support Application Update - Warrior Sol</title>
    <style>
      /* Same styles */
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; color: #333; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
      .email-wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #e88a49; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; }
      .section { padding: 30px 20px; text-align: left; }
      .section h1 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #e88a49; }
      .section p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .footer {
        background-color: #fff5ee;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .social-links a {
        color: #e88a49;
        margin: 0 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .social-links a:hover { color: #d67a39; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Hello <%= familyName %> Family,</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h1>Your Application Has Been Reviewed</h1>
        <p>
          We appreciate the time and trust you placed in Warrior Sol by applying for
          <strong><%= supportType.replace("_", " ").toUpperCase() %></strong> support.
        </p>
        <p>
          After careful review, we regret to inform you that your application was not approved at this time.
        </p>

        <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
        <p><%= message %></p>
        <% } %>

        <p>
          Please know that this decision does not reflect your worth or story. We encourage you to reapply in the future or explore other available resources in the Warrior Sol community.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: 24px">
          <p>Sending strength, light, and love. ðŸŒ»</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Stay connected</p>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/warriorsol">Instagram</a> |
          <a href="https://twitter.com/warriorsol">Twitter</a> |
          <a href="https://facebook.com/warriorsol">Facebook</a>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Warrior Sol. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
